Description:
  TheCommentsSubscriptions: generators will copy files to install TheComments 3.0 into your App

  Usage: [bundle exec] rails g the_comments_subscriptions OPTION_NAME
  Usage: [bundle exec] rails g the_comments_subscriptions:views OPTION_NAME

# MIGRATIONS:
  > rake the_comments_subscriptions_engine:install:migrations

# This text:
  > rails g the_comments_subscriptions --help

# Main generators:
  > rails g the_comments_subscriptions install

  This will create:
    app/models/comment_subscription.rb
    app/controllers/comment_subscriptions_controller.rb
    config/locales/en.the_comments_subscriptions.yml
    config/locales/ru.the_comments_subscriptions.yml

# Model generators:
  > rails g the_comments_subscriptions models

  This will generate:
    app/models/comment_subscription.rb

# Controller generators:
  > rails g the_comments_subscriptions controllers

  This will create:
    app/controllers/comment_subscriptions_controller.rb

# Mailers generators:
  > rails g the_comments_subscriptions mailers

  This will generate:
    app/mailers/comment_subscriber_mailer.rb

# Jobs generators:
  > rails g the_comments_subscriptions jobs

  This will generate:
    app/jobs/the_comments_subscriptions_job.rb

# Locales generators:
  > rails g the_comments_subscriptions locales

  This will generate:
    config/locales/en.the_comments_subscriptions.yml
    config/locales/ru.the_comments_subscriptions.yml

# All generators:
  > rails g the_comments_subscriptions all

  This will generate:
    app/models/comment_subscription.rb
    app/controllers/comment_subscriptions_controller.rb
    app/mailers/comment_subscriber_mailer.rb
    app/jobs/the_comments_subscriptions_job.rb
    config/locales/en.the_comments_subscriptions.yml
    config/locales/ru.the_comments_subscriptions.yml

# View Generators:
  > rails g the_comments_subscriptions:views install
    This will generate:
      app/views/the_comments/slim/mailers/new_comment.html.slim
      app/views/the_comments/slim/subscriptions/info.html.slim
